<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Config_Xml does not correctly handle flat lists. Take the following example:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
value1value2</code></pre>

<p>When accessing this XML config with Zend_Config only the path list-&gt;item is there and points to "value2" ("value1" has been overwritten), not list[0]. SimpleXml handles such flat lists completely correct.</p>

